General.Name: DPS Resources Bhd
General.Description: DPS Resources Berhad, an investment holding company, manufactures and trades in rubber wood furniture and roof trusses. It operates through seven segments: Investment Holding, Manufacturing, Trading, Property Development Services, Construction Services, Rental Income, and Real Estate. In addition, the company offers provision of saw milling, kiln-drying, and wood treatment services; real property, construction, and housing development, as well as real estate agency businesses; and furniture trading activities. It has operations in Malaysia, the United States, Europe, the Asia Pacific, and the Middle East. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Bukit Rambai, Malaysia.
